        <h2 class="font-display text-3xl md:text-4xl font-medium text-midnight mb-12 text-center">
          Bartholomäus Dedersen
        </h2>
        
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-start">
          <!-- Text content on the left -->
          <div class="space-y-6 px-5 md:px-0 order-2 lg:order-1">
            <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 font-medium">
              Co-Founder & IT
            </p>

            <div class="space-y-4">
              <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-gray-700">
                Bartholomäus is my strategic partner and the technical force behind Phialo Design. He manages the entire IT infrastructure of our website and ensures that our digital presence is always up to date.
              </p>

              <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-gray-700">
                As a creative sparring partner, we work together on refining concepts and scripts. His technical expertise and artistic understanding form a perfect complement to my craft work.
              </p>

              <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-gray-700">
                With his many years of experience in IT and video production, he not only supports the technical side but also brings valuable perspectives to artistic collaboration and consulting.
              </p>
            </div>

